msgstr "La vérification de sécurité a échoué. Veuillez réessayer."

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:208
msgid "Settings saved."
msgstr "Paramètres enregistrés."

#: includes/class-micro-site-care-post-last-updated-date-settings.php:213
msgid "Settings"
